    <div class="footer-content">
      <div class="container">

        <div class="row g-5">
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <h3 class="footer-heading">About Poor Chefs</h3>
            <p>Who are we? We're the poor chefs in the college towns around the country. We don't have the money or time to think about what to eat every day, but together, we will have that time. We're all about helping college students find a platform for easy recipes that they can make on the go or late at night. Share your favorite dorm room recipes and let others in on the yumminess. Happy cooking!</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-6 col-lg-2">
            <h3 class="footer-heading">Navigation</h3>
            <ul class="footer-links list-unstyled">
              <li><a href="/"><i class="bi bi-chevron-right"></i> Home</a></li>
              <li><a href="/"><i class="bi bi-chevron-right"></i> My Recipes</a></li>
              <li><a href="/login"><i class="bi bi-chevron-right"></i> Log In</a></li>
            </ul>
